name: Catke
description: Catke ($CATKE) is the world’s most careless and arrogant cat—yet somehow everyone wants to be its friend. Built on Binance Smart Chain, Catke isn’t just a meme; it’s a community-driven movement that blends humor, heart, and purpose. Behind the laughs lies a mission to support stray animals and shelters worldwide. Holders join a playful yet passionate collective determined to make CATKE the next global meme icon—one friendship, one cat meme, and one shelter donation at a time.
